## Summary

This documentation covers the Behavioral Cohorts API (v3/v5) which provides endpoints for listing, downloading, uploading, and updating user cohorts in Amplitude using HTTP basic authentication with asynchronous download operations requiring three-step process (request, poll status, download file).

